reviewText: I RUN A PICK UR OWN APPLE OPERATION ALONG WITH A PUMPKIN PATCH, WE USED THEM IN FALL OF 2012 AND THEY WERE VERY WILL RECEIVED, ESPECIALLY BY SCHOOL GROUPS OF YOUNGER CHILDREN. WE WILL REORDER IN 2013.

My son, age 3, loves this video.  He buys apples everytime we go to the grocery store since we bought it.  The video takes you on a detailed tour of an apple orchard, an apple sorting facility, an apple pie filling factory, and an apple cider factory.  I own five farming videos, and this is by far the best and the most entertaining.  It also includes an apple theme song throughout the video, which he loves to sing.
